{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_10_01_short",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 思い入れのある曲 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらくした頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after Moon Tempest became BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "地方でのフェスに出演して、すぐに戻って\n新曲のMV撮影……分かっていてもやはり忙しないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Performing at a countryside festival and filming a new song's MV\nright after returning… I knew it‚ but it's really hectic.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "タクシーが来るまで少しでも休んでおこう\n体調はどうだ？　何かあったらすぐに言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's rest as much as we can until the taxi comes.\nHow are you feeling? Tell me right away if anything happens.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.53333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "この程度なんともありませんわ\n自ら望んだスケジュールですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is nothing.\nIt's a schedule I wanted myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.1999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってからはずっとこんな日々が\n続いていますもの。すっかり慣れましたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since becoming BIG4‚ it’s been like this\nall the time. I'm completely used to it now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それに……フェスから帰る前に麻奈様のお墓参りも\nさせていただけましたから。感謝していますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides… I was also able to visit Mana-sama's grave\nbefore returning from the festival. I'm grateful for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.4999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様に現況を報告して……\n初心に返ることが出来ましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I reported the current situation to Mana-sama…\nand I was able to return to my original intentions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "念願のBIG4になったとはいえ\n微塵も油断することなく邁進してまいりますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though we've become the long-awaited BIG4‚\nI’ll keep moving forward and never let my guard down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.4999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると\n時間を作った甲斐があったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me happy to hear you say that.\nIt was worth making the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}さん\n来月には月ストの単独ライブがありますわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}-san‚\nthere's a Moon Tempest solo live coming up next month‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4932137984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.5999999483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "その時のセンターをどうするかについて\nお話……と言うよりは、決意表明がありますの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About the center position for that…\nI'd like to say… No‚ I have a declaration of resolve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.5666666667
    }
  ]
}